== TitanChat Supports

TitanChat Supports, the TitanChat addons for plugin supports

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

=== Features

* Easy to write

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

=== Functions

* Supporting other plugins

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

=== Addons
* Installation: Place into /plugins/TitanChat/addons/

==== ChatLog
* Logs Player chat
* Creates chat.log in /plugins/TitanChat/

==== FactionsHook
* Hooks into Factions
* Adds 2 new variables
** //%ftitle// - **Factions Title**
** //%faction// - **Faction**

==== Filter
* Filters words and phrases
* Entirely configurable

==== RangeChannels
* Contains 3 range based channels
** Local
** World
** Global
* Each can be configured

==== TimeStamp
* Shows the current time
* Configurable timestamp format

==== TownyHook
* Hooks into Towny
* Adds 8 new variables
** //%ttitle// - **Towny Title**
** //%tsurname// - **Towny Surname**
** //%town// - **Town Name
**
** //%townformatted// - **Formatted Town Name**
** //%towntag// - **Town Tag**
** //%nation// - **Nation Name**
** //%nationformatted// - **Formatted Nation Name**
** //%nationtag// - **Nation Tag**

=== Custom Channels
* Installation: Place into /plugins/TitanChat/addons/channels/



=== Commands
* Installation: Place into /plugins/TitanChat/addons/commands/

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

=== Dependecies

* TitanChat
* NC-LoaderLib
* Whatever plugin that you are supporting

